snippet.title: The first look of DESTINY SAGA
snippet.description:
Welcome to our channel 
DESTINY SAGA is a roguelike action role-playing game with beautiful pixel art style. Players will take on the role of protagonist Rosen and explore the dangerous St.Noah continent to find the source of the Xorc crisis. The first worldwide test is coming. See you on April 19!
